"tasks, :guilabel:`On-time Rate` for deliveries, :guilabel:`Invoiced` information, "
":guilabel:`Vendor Bills`, and the :guilabel:`Partner Ledger` connected to this contact."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:241
