msgid "|IAP| services are provided by Odoo, as well as third-parties, and have a wide range of uses."
msgstr "|IAP| service များကို Odoo နှင့် third-party များက ပံ့ပိုးပြီး အသုံးပြုပုံ အမျိုးမျိုး ရှိသည်။"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/in_app_purchase.rst:35
msgid "The following |IAP| services are offered by Odoo:"
